milestones.description: John Davison and Umar Bhatti's 31-run partnership is CAN's highest for the 8th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 24 between Ashish Bagai and Sanjayan Thuraisingam
This is the lowest match aggregate (268) involving teams Bermuda & Canada in ODIs
Canada's 57-run win against Bermuda is the smallest margin of victory in terms of runs in ODIs, beating 60-run win against Bangladesh
Dean Minors has broken the record for most dismissals (11) in ODIs for BMUDA, going past Kwame Tucker's 9
Mukuddem has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (15) for BMUDA, going past Romaine
